ji\" /><br />\n香港果班fans真係唔夠養佢地<br />\n<br />\n仲有最大問題係4大唱片公司+4個台全部都仆街陷家鏟黎<br />\n同香港政府d仆街圍標拎曝光率同獎項一樣<br />\n全撚部收買翻黎"},{"pid":"ff15f3c4f86b46d10ab2f11723ef94127209114d","tid":1880303,"uid":32883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bf9750293c91d5a8651b30898e3a4b0b04c53435","tid":1880303,"uid":27210,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"2efd61729906c1ab45b23e73b1d93f743f7dd411","tid":1880303,"uid":32883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:33:52.000Z","msg":"因為地下音樂一旦商業化就會變質 hiphop同commercially係無可能並存"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:35:33.000Z","msg":"全世界都係咁架啦<br />\n唔淨止香港架喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:40:41.000Z","msg":"所以我會寧願indie band/singer/rapper繼續indie 咁先係真係既hiphop culture 從來hiphop最重要既係佢文化背景同思想 強國個d咩終國有嘻哈就係最好既反面教材 真係得啖笑 得個殼 成件事都同hiphop本意背道而馳 如果咁樣先會多人聽 我就真係不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e07dc121917212ad6879eace72cc66ff21b13810","tid":1880303,"uid":186882,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"92c38db8eb27a58f6efbc81bd091fe444aee1fbd","tid":1880303,"uid":2357,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"5b7a8b21a30a11133d0288020d364c14eb92a56b","tid":1880303,"uid":36817,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:37:06.000Z","msg":"你見TTN 而家都就黎收皮都知其實一直indie 係香港真係搵唔到錢<br />\n一黎觀眾群少  多後生聽kpop<br />\n二黎孕育indie band 既地方都無咩<br />\n<br />\n一個武漢肺炎就就快交唔起租<br />\n連TTN 都做唔住既話 indie 就快步入寒冬"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:38:13.000Z","msg":"好撚sad, 整個indie界好傷"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:40:52.000Z","msg":"舊年攪革命今年又瘟疫<br />\n你睇show既機會都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"862233b9089f75df7ab3cee2d45eb2f99842f2c9","tid":1880303,"uid":27991,"like":2,"dislike":3,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:41:33.000Z","msg":"由以前 90 年代 Anodize, Huh, AMk, Black &amp; Blue 年代<br />\nIndie 上唔到水面講到而加 2020 <br />\n<br />\n唔好賴聽眾質素, 係好多 indie band 本身技不如人<br />\n各位可以去 youtube 搵返以前 90, 2000 年代既 Band sound<br />\n好多寫歌水平, 彈奏技術都好雞, 完全上唔到大台<br />\n唔係唔支持佢地, 係支持唔落<br />\n<br />\n到近呢 10 年, 可能科技進步,錄音比前簡單方便<br />\n但 indie band 唔見有明顯進步<br />\n好似多左 band 出黎, 但來來去去都係個啲 style<br />\n技術都係 Rubber Band 比較好<br />\n<br />\n而加玩 indie 野, 玩 band 多左渠道推廣自己<br />\nYoutube, Facebook, Instagram, Spotify, Apple Music <br />\n如果真係覺得自己懷才不遇, 香港人唔欣賞自己<br />\n可以擺歌上去, 有實力既一定有人睇到"},{"pid":"34514e0de06f9880b07ca50cac55acd258b922a1","tid":1880303,"uid":27210,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"bdf5a583d13e3dc0e0bdc1ebef552187f8bd4a6b","tid":1880303,"uid":32883,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c50a88c8a2c02fe4164477d4650fa1e242fdc825","tid":1880303,"uid":27210,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"39a7f26a91acd435665713e7c4ae90ce82560302","tid":1880303,"uid":228143,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:31:12.000Z","msg":"音樂一直係貴族玩既野<br />\n<br />\n唔係普通人唱下歌就到歌手<br />\n<br />\n果d叫代唱 唔係歌手<br />\n<br />\n香港所謂既一線歌手都係代唱多<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n你叫佢地分析番首歌都講唔出<br />\n<br />\n樂理 編曲 層次全部要讀好多野<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:32:36.000Z","msg":"Band仔窮到仆街<br />\n樂理 編曲 層次好過你一線歌手好撚多"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:36:28.000Z","msg":"奈何香港人唔識欣賞indie band 中年既一輩甚至話鄧麗君個d先叫唱歌 而家既歌手都唔知唱乜鳩 <br />\n香港真係邊行邊業都脫離唔到老屎忽<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T14:46:24.000Z","msg":"Band 自然有年輕人市場啦<br />\n問題係你主流band得咁少<br />\n仲要啲嘢唔係好band sound <br />\n無聽開既好難會接觸到"},{"pid":"aec6d4f6c8a7